Ask HN: Who owns the newsyc100 (and similar) Twitter bots?
text:
Longtime follower (and appreciator!) of @newsyc100 but looks like it (and the similar ones with different thresholds) hasn't tweeted in a few days (since the 25th). The account doesn't have twitter DMs enabled or indicate who owns it. Searching github didn't yield anything promising.
Anyone know who owns it? Seems perhaps they're unaware it's broken so would like to let them know.
https://twitter.com/newsyc100
